==Personal==
The son of Radim Ne<U+010D>as, also called [[Radim Ne<U+010D>as (born 1988)|Radim]], is also a professional footballer.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fotbal.idnes.cz/duklu-tahnou-synove-slavnych-otcu-hasek-rada-berger-a-necas-po8-/fot_dsouteze.aspx?c=A110521_115517_fot_dsouteze_pes |title=Duklu t<U+00E1>hnou synov<U+00E9> slavn<U+00FD>ch otc<U+016F>: Ha<U+0161>ek, Rada, Berger a Ne<U+010D>as {{cs icon}}|work=idnes.cz|publisher=Mlad<U+00E1> fronta DNES|date=21 May 2011|accessdate=28 January 2012}}</ref>

